        useCase: 'Code review, refactoring decisions, learning',
        bestModel: 'Claude Sonnet, ChatGPT-4'
      },
      {
        title: 'Bug Analysis',
        description: 'Multi-angle debugging approach',
        prompt: `Analyze this bug from three perspectives:

BUG DESCRIPTION:
[Describe the bug, error messages, steps to reproduce]

