        useCase: 'Research, decision-making, learning',
        bestModel: 'Claude Sonnet, ChatGPT-4'
      },
      {
        title: 'Red Team Your Idea',
        description: 'Find weaknesses in your plans',
        prompt: `I want to red team this idea/plan:

